      caddc a1i sylancr syl3anc wne recoscl recnd resincl mulcl sylanbrc divdir
      clt wbr rpne0 syl112anc oveq2d syl22anc oveq12d eqtrd oveq1d 3eqtr3d nnre
      cz nnz remulcl rpexpcl 3eqtrd eqtr3d fveq2d oveq2 wf1 adantr 2nn0 elfznn0
      fzfid cle nn0mulcl nn0re wb ad2antrr 2re 2pos pm3.2i mpbid mpbird ex nncn
      elfzelz ad2antrl simprr 2ne0 ax-mp ovex fvmpt sylan rpre fznn0sub reexpcl
      2cn sylan2 wo i2 oveq1i nn0ge0 divge0 mpanr12 nn0cn divcan2 eqeltrrd expr
