      ctan addcl simpld elrp expdiv simprd gt0ne0 tanval recdiv eqtr2d demoivre
      syl121anc divcan4 divass cmpt crn wf1o copab elfzle2 lep1 syl6breqr letrd
      lemul2 cuz nn0uz syl6eleq elfz5 fznn0sub2 zcn ssriv sseldi subcan dom2lem
      mulcan bitrd df-mpt f1eq1 sylibr f1f1orn eqid wf wss f1f frn sselda bccl2
