    $( Lemma for ~ basel .  Using ~ vieta1 , we can calculate the sum of the
       roots of ` P ` as the quotient of the top two coefficients, and since
       the function ` T ` enumerates the roots, we are left with an equation
       that sums the ` cot ^ 2 ` function at the ` M ` different roots. $)
