    basel.g $e |- G = ( n e. NN |-> ( 1 / ( ( 2 x. n ) + 1 ) ) ) $.
    $( Lemma for ~ basel .  The function ` G ` goes to zero because it is
       bounded by ` 1 / n ` . $)
    basellem6 $p |- G ~~> 0 $=
      ( cc0 wbr wtru cn c1 cdiv co cc wcel a1i c2 caddc cr wceq adantl syl cle
